CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Silicom Ltd designs and manufactures networking and data infrastructure solutions for various servers, server based systems and communications devices. Its product categories consist of Server Adapters; Edge Networking Solutions; FPGA Based Cards; x86 Open Appliances and Bypass Switches and TAPs. Geographically, it derives a majority of revenue from North America and also has a presence in Europe and Asia-Pacific.
